<span class="header1">Business/Management paired with Public Service (CG)</span>

<p>If you scored high in the "C" and "G" categories, you are people-oriented. You have leadership ability and can persuade others. You feel a responsibility to others. You probably want to work in ways that can help your friends, your family and your community.</p>
<p>Most occupations in this pairing require at least a Bachelor's Degree. In some of these jobs, it helps to have a Master's Degree or a Ph.D.</p>

<p><strong>Here are some career possibilities for you to explore.</strong></p>

